        No need to design device control solutions from scratch.
        Lelylan created the new <code>&lt;device&gt;</code>
        directive (aka HTML5 Web Componets) that offers a beautiful and customizable solution
        to create web apps across desktop, tablet, and mobile for the Connected Home in minutes.
        </p>
        <%= image_tag 'device-directive.png' %>
        <p><a class="button-add" href="http://lelylan.github.io/device-directive-ng/">Get started with the device component &rarr;</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="right small">
        <%= image_tag 'companies/apps.png' %>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <hr/>
    </div>


    <div class="inner row">
      <div class="left big">
        <h2>Lelylan dashboard</h2>
        <p>
        It lets you create, simulate, monitor and control connected products in realtime in the
